mbti_signals.shift_explanation: Showed more T than usual when demanding informed decision-making and analytical rigor. Slight J shift when insisting on proper framework before proceeding.

big5_signals.notable: Higher conscientiousness than baseline - wanted thorough analysis before decisions

learnings: User's avoidance is delivery confidence, not customer rejection fear
User wants partnership in decision-making, not just pushing toward action
User will call out incomplete frameworks and demand better analysis
User appreciates direct feedback but wants thorough thinking behind it

meta_observations.what_worked: Direct challenging of avoidance patterns, identifying delivery confidence issue
meta_observations.what_didnt: Avoiding readiness analysis, pushing for speed over informed decisions
